ce June: I have, as far as I recollect, described Lydia’s hiding it.… Pity I didn’t bury a balalaika somewhere too, so as to give them the pleasure of imagining a Slavic murder to the clinking of goblets and the singing of “Pazhaláy zhemen-áh, dara-gúy-ah.…” “Do take pity of me, dear.…”

